[
    {
        "text": "\"The Science of Us\" presents \"The Positives of Negative Thinking.\"",
        "startTime": 89,
        "endTime": 4251,
        "slowStartTime": 284,
        "slowEndTime": 6601
    },
    {
        "text": "Everywhere you look, people are urging you to be positive.",
        "startTime": 5141,
        "endTime": 8019,
        "slowStartTime": 7861,
        "slowEndTime": 12254
    },
    {
        "text": "Telling you that you're more likely to achieve your goals...",
        "startTime": 8359,
        "endTime": 10955,
        "slowStartTime": 12688,
        "slowEndTime": 16658
    },
    {
        "text": "...if you think you're definitely going to achieve them.",
        "startTime": 11031,
        "endTime": 13308,
        "slowStartTime": 16697,
        "slowEndTime": 20187
    },
    {
        "text": "But here's a surprise in scientific finding.",
        "startTime": 13427,
        "endTime": 15774,
        "slowStartTime": 20291,
        "slowEndTime": 23886
    },
    {
        "text": "Optimism can actually hold you back, and a little bit of pessimism can be a big help.",
        "startTime": 16042,
        "endTime": 21578,
        "slowStartTime": 24213,
        "slowEndTime": 32592
    },
    {
        "text": "That idea comes from the work of Gabriele Oettingen,...",
        "startTime": 22128,
        "endTime": 24884,
        "slowStartTime": 33342,
        "slowEndTime": 37551
    },
    {
        "text": "...a German psychologist who's been studying optimism since the 1980s.",
        "startTime": 25075,
        "endTime": 28943,
        "slowStartTime": 37762,
        "slowEndTime": 43639
    },
    {
        "text": "In 1991, she studied a group of women in a weight loss program.",
        "startTime": 29729,
        "endTime": 33606,
        "slowStartTime": 44744,
        "slowEndTime": 50634
    },
    {
        "text": "Before the program began, she asked them to predict how well they'd do...",
        "startTime": 33889,
        "endTime": 37669,
        "slowStartTime": 50984,
        "slowEndTime": 56728
    },
    {
        "text": "...and she was shocked to find that the women who were pessimistic about losing weight,...",
        "startTime": 37853,
        "endTime": 41765,
        "slowStartTime": 56930,
        "slowEndTime": 62873
    },
    {
        "text": "...who thought the process would be difficult and that they might not succeed,...",
        "startTime": 41918,
        "endTime": 45460,
        "slowStartTime": 63027,
        "slowEndTime": 68415
    },
    {
        "text": "...actually ended up losing an average of 24 more pounds than the positive thinkers.",
        "startTime": 45817,
        "endTime": 50624,
        "slowStartTime": 68876,
        "slowEndTime": 76161
    },
    {
        "text": "Over and over again, she found that positive fantasies...",
        "startTime": 51351,
        "endTime": 54421,
        "slowStartTime": 77177,
        "slowEndTime": 81856
    },
    {
        "text": "...didn't help people achieve their goals.",
        "startTime": 54548,
        "endTime": 56477,
        "slowStartTime": 81972,
        "slowEndTime": 84940
    },
    {
        "text": "And in fact, often got in the way.",
        "startTime": 56649,
        "endTime": 58449,
        "slowStartTime": 85123,
        "slowEndTime": 87899
    },
    {
        "text": "Here's her theory about why.",
        "startTime": 58793,
        "endTime": 60227,
        "slowStartTime": 88339,
        "slowEndTime": 90565
    },
    {
        "text": "When you indulge in starry-eyed dreaming about the future,...",
        "startTime": 60644,
        "endTime": 63844,
        "slowStartTime": 91116,
        "slowEndTime": 95991
    },
    {
        "text": "...you start ignoring the tasks in front of you.",
        "startTime": 64123,
        "endTime": 66241,
        "slowStartTime": 96334,
        "slowEndTime": 99587
    },
    {
        "text": "Instead of pushing yourself to go to the gym or study for a test,...",
        "startTime": 66605,
        "endTime": 69839,
        "slowStartTime": 100057,
        "slowEndTime": 104984
    },
    {
        "text": "...you just happily imagine having big muscles or good grades,...",
        "startTime": 70211,
        "endTime": 73743,
        "slowStartTime": 105467,
        "slowEndTime": 110840
    },
    {
        "text": "...and don't feel much motivation to get to work.",
        "startTime": 73911,
        "endTime": 76143,
        "slowStartTime": 111016,
        "slowEndTime": 114440
    }
]